A company called Atari made the game in 1982, and it quickly became notorious for being one of the worst video games ever created. The game was heavily criticized for its poor design, confusing gameplay, and numerous glitches. It was such a commercial failure that Atari allegedly buried thousands of unsold copies in a landfill in New Mexico.
